title: 241: 10 Takeaways from the College Football season
itunes:title: 241: 10 Takeaways from the College Football season
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap Pittsburgh's resilient Monday Night Football win over the Cincinnati (00:53). The guys also debate the Playoff Committee's selections (7:47) before diving into ten scouting takeaways from the college regular season (12:12).
